race.comment: JEWELS CAPTAIN (4) resumes and looks to have come on nicely during the break, sharpening up with strong work in readiness. Was an eye-catcher when fresh last campaign and can return with a bang. RENEGADE CHIEF (5) bounced back here last time with a brave on-pace placing. Peaking now and reunited with Milnes, expect him to roll forward and give another bold sight. ARLO'S DREAM (1) was only fair when resuming here two weeks ago but strips fitter and is capable of playing a role. SOCIAL DANCER (11) hasn't threatened in two runs back off a long break but will be fitter third-up and gets in well at the weights with the 3kg claimer. Not to be dismissed.
